data.description: This beautiful Shelby Homes, LLC Home has everything you could want. With 2320 sq ft of living space with 4 bedrooms and 2 baths! Huge open floor plan with vaulted ceiling in living room. This house includes granite countertops, wood look ceramic tile floors, custom cabinets, custom tile backsplash in the kitchen, raised ceilings, stainless steel built -in appliances, two wood burning fire places, multiple dining areas, and much more. Builder to supply 20 pallets of sod, landscape package, full sprinkler, and privacy fence. Located in Amata Tera, Troy ISD! Home is a must see! Builder will include 20x40 shop/barn that will match the exterior of the home, with roll up door, slab floor, electrical outlets, and fluorescent lighting.
